12127
12128bool
12129common_handle_option_auto (struct gcc_options *opts,
12130 struct gcc_options *opts_set,
12131 const struct cl_decoded_option *decoded,
12132 unsigned int lang_mask, int kind,
12133 location_t loc,
12134 const struct cl_option_handlers *handlers,
12135 diagnostic_context *dc)
12136{
12137 size_t scode = decoded->opt_index;
12138 int value = decoded->value;
12139 enum opt_code code = (enum opt_code) scode;
12140
12141 gcc_assert (decoded->canonical_option_num_elements <= 2);
12142
12143 switch (code)
12144 {
12145 case OPT_Wextra:
12146 if (!opts_set->x_warn_clobbered)
12147 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12148 OPT_Wclobbered, NULL, value,
12149 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12150 if (!opts_set->x_warn_empty_body)
12151 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12152 OPT_Wempty_body, NULL, value,
12153 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12154 if (!opts_set->x_cpp_warn_expansion_to_defined)
12155 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12156 OPT_Wexpansion_to_defined, NULL, value,
12157 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12158 if (!opts_set->x_warn_ignored_qualifiers)
12159 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12160 OPT_Wignored_qualifiers, NULL, value,
12161 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12162 if (!opts_set->x_warn_missing_field_initializers)
12163 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12164 OPT_Wmissing_field_initializers, NULL, value,
12165 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12166 if (!opts_set->x_warn_missing_parameter_type)
12167 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12168 OPT_Wmissing_parameter_type, NULL, value,
12169 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12170 if (!opts_set->x_warn_old_style_declaration)
12171 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12172 OPT_Wold_style_declaration, NULL, value,
12173 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12174 if (!opts_set->x_warn_override_init)
12175 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12176 OPT_Woverride_init, NULL, value,
12177 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12178 if (!opts_set->x_warn_sign_compare)
12179 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12180 OPT_Wsign_compare, NULL, value,
12181 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12182 if (!opts_set->x_warn_sized_deallocation)
12183 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12184 OPT_Wsized_deallocation, NULL, value,
12185 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12186 if (!opts_set->x_warn_type_limits)
12187 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12188 OPT_Wtype_limits, NULL, value,
12189 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12190 if (!opts_set->x_warn_uninitialized)
12191 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12192 OPT_Wuninitialized, NULL, value,
12193 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12194 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_but_set_parameter)
12195 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12196 OPT_Wunused_but_set_parameter, NULL, (opts->x_warn_unused && opts->x_extra_warnings),
12197 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12198 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_parameter)
12199 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12200 OPT_Wunused_parameter, NULL, (opts->x_warn_unused && opts->x_extra_warnings),
12201 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12202 break;
12203
12204 case OPT_Wpedantic:
12205 if (!opts_set->x_cpp_warn_expansion_to_defined)
12206 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12207 OPT_Wexpansion_to_defined, NULL, value,
12208 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12209 break;
12210
12211 case OPT_Wuninitialized:
12212 if (!opts_set->x_warn_maybe_uninitialized)
12213 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12214 OPT_Wmaybe_uninitialized, NULL, value,
12215 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12216 break;
12217
12218 case OPT_Wshadow:
12219 if (!opts_set->x_warn_shadow_ivar)
12220 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12221 OPT_Wshadow_ivar, NULL, value,
12222 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12223 if (!opts_set->x_warn_shadow_local)
12224 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12225 OPT_Wshadow_local, NULL, value,
12226 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12227 break;
12228
12229 case OPT_Wshadow_local:
12230 if (!opts_set->x_warn_shadow_compatible_local)
12231 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12232 OPT_Wshadow_compatible_local, NULL, value,
12233 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12234 break;
12235
12236 case OPT_Wunused:
12237 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_but_set_parameter)
12238 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12239 OPT_Wunused_but_set_parameter, NULL, (opts->x_warn_unused && opts->x_extra_warnings),
12240 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12241 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_but_set_variable)
12242 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12243 OPT_Wunused_but_set_variable, NULL, value,
12244 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12245 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_function)
12246 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12247 OPT_Wunused_function, NULL, value,
12248 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12249 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_label)
12250 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12251 OPT_Wunused_label, NULL, value,
12252 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12253 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_local_typedefs)
12254 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12255 OPT_Wunused_local_typedefs, NULL, value,
12256 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12257 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_parameter)
12258 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12259 OPT_Wunused_parameter, NULL, (opts->x_warn_unused && opts->x_extra_warnings),
12260 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12261 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_value)
12262 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12263 OPT_Wunused_value, NULL, value,
12264 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12265 if (!opts_set->x_warn_unused_variable)
12266 handle_generated_option (opts, opts_set,
12267 OPT_Wunused_variable, NULL, value,
12268 lang_mask, kind, loc, handlers, true, dc);
12269 break;
12270
12271 default:
12272 break;
12273 }
12274 return true;
12275}

12278
12279bool
12280BRIG_handle_option_auto (struct gcc_options *opts ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12281 struct gcc_options *opts_set ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12282 size_t scode ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED, const char *arg ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED, int value ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12283 unsigned int lang_mask ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED, int kind ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12284 location_t loc ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12285 const struct cl_option_handlers *handlers ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12286 diagnostic_context *dc ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED)
12287{
12288 enum opt_code code = (enum opt_code) scode;
12289
12290 switch (code)
12291 {
12292 default:
12293 break;
12294 }
12295 return true;
12296}

12299
12300bool
12301C_handle_option_auto (struct gcc_options *opts ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12302 struct gcc_options *opts_set ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,
12303 size_t scode ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED, const char *arg ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED, int value ATTRIBUTE_UNUSED,

13586#include "cpplib.h"
13587void
13588cpp_handle_option_auto (const struct gcc_options * opts,
13589 size_t scode, struct cpp_options * cpp_opts)
13590{
13591 enum opt_code code = (enum opt_code) scode;
13592
13593 switch (code)
13594 {
13595 case OPT_Wbuiltin_macro_redefined:
13596 cpp_opts->warn_builtin_macro_redefined = opts->x_cpp_warn_builtin_macro_redefined;
13597 break;
13598 case OPT_Wc___compat:
13599 cpp_opts->warn_cxx_operator_names = opts->x_warn_cxx_compat;
13600 break;
13601 case OPT_Wc__11_compat:
13602 cpp_opts->cpp_warn_cxx11_compat = opts->x_warn_cxx11_compat;
13603 break;
13604 case OPT_Wc90_c99_compat:
13605 cpp_opts->cpp_warn_c90_c99_compat = opts->x_warn_c90_c99_compat;
13606 break;
13607 case OPT_Wcomment:
13608 cpp_opts->warn_comments = opts->x_cpp_warn_comment;
13609 break;
13610 case OPT_Wdate_time:
13611 cpp_opts->warn_date_time = opts->x_cpp_warn_date_time;
13612 break;
13613 case OPT_Wdeprecated:
13614 cpp_opts->cpp_warn_deprecated = opts->x_warn_deprecated;
13615 break;
13616 case OPT_Wendif_labels:
13617 cpp_opts->warn_endif_labels = opts->x_cpp_warn_endif_labels;
13618 break;
13619 case OPT_Wexpansion_to_defined:
13620 cpp_opts->warn_expansion_to_defined = opts->x_cpp_warn_expansion_to_defined;
13621 break;
13622 case OPT_Winvalid_pch:
13623 cpp_opts->warn_invalid_pch = opts->x_cpp_warn_invalid_pch;
13624 break;
13625 case OPT_Wliteral_suffix:
13626 cpp_opts->warn_literal_suffix = opts->x_cpp_warn_literal_suffix;
13627 break;
13628 case OPT_Wlong_long:
13629 cpp_opts->cpp_warn_long_long = opts->x_warn_long_long;
13630 break;
13631 case OPT_Wmissing_include_dirs:
13632 cpp_opts->warn_missing_include_dirs = opts->x_cpp_warn_missing_include_dirs;
13633 break;
13634 case OPT_Wmultichar:
13635 cpp_opts->warn_multichar = opts->x_cpp_warn_multichar;
13636 break;
13637 case OPT_Wnormalized_:
13638 cpp_opts->warn_normalize = opts->x_cpp_warn_normalize;
13639 break;
13640 case OPT_Wpedantic:
13641 cpp_opts->cpp_pedantic = opts->x_pedantic;
13642 break;
13643 case OPT_Wtraditional:
13644 cpp_opts->cpp_warn_traditional = opts->x_warn_traditional;
13645 break;
13646 case OPT_Wtrigraphs:
13647 cpp_opts->warn_trigraphs = opts->x_cpp_warn_trigraphs;
13648 break;
13649 case OPT_Wundef:
13650 cpp_opts->warn_undef = opts->x_cpp_warn_undef;
13651 break;
13652 case OPT_Wvariadic_macros:
13653 cpp_opts->warn_variadic_macros = opts->x_cpp_warn_variadic_macros;
13654 break;
13655 default:
13656 break;
13657 }
13658}

13660void
13661init_global_opts_from_cpp(struct gcc_options * opts,
13662 const struct cpp_options * cpp_opts)
13663{
13664 opts->x_cpp_warn_builtin_macro_redefined = cpp_opts->warn_builtin_macro_redefined;
13665 opts->x_warn_cxx_compat = cpp_opts->warn_cxx_operator_names;
13666 opts->x_warn_cxx11_compat = cpp_opts->cpp_warn_cxx11_compat;
13667 opts->x_warn_c90_c99_compat = cpp_opts->cpp_warn_c90_c99_compat;
13668 opts->x_cpp_warn_comment = cpp_opts->warn_comments;
13669 opts->x_cpp_warn_date_time = cpp_opts->warn_date_time;
13670 opts->x_warn_deprecated = cpp_opts->cpp_warn_deprecated;
13671 opts->x_cpp_warn_endif_labels = cpp_opts->warn_endif_labels;
13672 opts->x_cpp_warn_expansion_to_defined = cpp_opts->warn_expansion_to_defined;
13673 opts->x_cpp_warn_invalid_pch = cpp_opts->warn_invalid_pch;
13674 opts->x_cpp_warn_literal_suffix = cpp_opts->warn_literal_suffix;
13675 opts->x_warn_long_long = cpp_opts->cpp_warn_long_long;
13676 opts->x_cpp_warn_missing_include_dirs = cpp_opts->warn_missing_include_dirs;
13677 opts->x_cpp_warn_multichar = cpp_opts->warn_multichar;
13678 opts->x_cpp_warn_normalize = cpp_opts->warn_normalize;
13679 opts->x_pedantic = cpp_opts->cpp_pedantic;
13680 opts->x_warn_traditional = cpp_opts->cpp_warn_traditional;
13681 opts->x_cpp_warn_trigraphs = cpp_opts->warn_trigraphs;
13682 opts->x_cpp_warn_undef = cpp_opts->warn_undef;
13683 opts->x_cpp_warn_variadic_macros = cpp_opts->warn_variadic_macros;
13684}
